    <readme><![CDATA[Frequently Asked Questions Module for Runway

- Can be used with or without Categories
- Can allow users to submit their own questions
- Can be setup to hide specific nodes from menu's or site map
- Uses Rich text editors for bigger customization
- Can be configured to use J-Query for simple sliding animation
]]></readme>
  </info>
